# 21. Authentication Database Design

Authentication is the foundation of every secured operation inside NEXORA AI.

The database must support:

- User Registration
- Login
- JWT Authentication
- Refresh Tokens
- Email Verification
- Password Reset
- Role Based Access Control
- Account Status Management
- Audit Tracking

Authentication should remain independent from Student, Recruiter, Company, and College modules.

---

# 22. Authentication Database Schema

Authentication consists of the following tables.

```
users

roles

refresh_tokens

email_verification_tokens

password_reset_tokens
```

Future versions may include

```
oauth_accounts

login_history

user_sessions

failed_login_attempts

devices
```

