# 24. User Entity

Purpose

Represents every authenticated account inside the platform.

The User entity is the parent entity of

- Student
- Recruiter
- College
- Administrator

No business-specific information should be stored here.

---

# 25. User Table

```
users
```

Columns

```
id

first_name

last_name

email

phone

password

role_id

status

email_verified

profile_picture

last_login

created_at

updated_at
```

